    "BEIR's HotpotQA dataset (Thakur et al., 2021; Yang et al., 2018) was selected for its reasonably sized documents.",
    "We randomly sampled five documents, stitching the first four together to form a stitched document (Figure 6), and keeping the fifth as a normal document (Figure 7.",
    "The document IDs are:",
    "• Stitched: 44547136, 14115210, 5580754, 54045118.",
    "• Normal: 30214079."
  ]
